room_title: Escape room "Lunar Escape" by Mission Escapes in Denver
review: My friends and I love doing escape rooms in AZ so when I was visiting a best friend in Denver we absolutely had to do one with her family. We did the Lunar Escape room and escaped with 4 mins to spare! The puzzles were very clever, we had unlimited hints, and we had a blast! Our GM was very helpful and it'd be fun to go back and try the other escape room!

room_title: Escape room "Lunar Escape" by Mission Escapes in Denver
review: Lunar Escape was the 7th or 8th escape room I've done.  Hands down my favorite.  The story was interesting, the clues were challenging but made sense, great room.

room_title: Escape room "Lunar Escape" by Mission Escapes in Denver
review: Mission Escapes has the best rooms in the Denver Area! I've done 21 different escape rooms and Lunar Escape is at the top of the list! A few of us went back to do Treasure Hunt and we had a blast doing that one as well. Open up more rooms!
